		</li>

		<li>
			<span class="text-warning"><i class="fa-li fas fa-caret-right"></i></span>
			<b>Recipes - </b>Here are a few recipes for some of the dishes commonly associated with the Passover meal.
			More will be added as we receive them.
			If you have any favorite recipes, send them along to us!
			<ul>
